00:14:04.760 --> 00:14:06.220
Note this down carefully.

00:14:09.160 --> 00:14:10.160
First was

00:14:10.160 --> 00:14:11.760
Lin Ran falling to his death.

00:14:11.800 --> 00:14:12.440
Then it was

00:14:12.640 --> 00:14:14.280
Li Xiaoru drowning.

00:14:15.240 --> 00:14:15.920
After that

00:14:15.920 --> 00:14:17.960
was Zhao Wenbing being tortured to death.

00:14:17.960 --> 00:14:19.360
Finally, I was poisoned.

00:14:19.800 --> 00:14:20.600
Is that all,

00:14:20.600 --> 00:14:21.130
officer?

00:14:31.720 --> 00:14:32.320
Hey, Zhai.

00:14:33.560 --> 00:14:36.020
How's the investigation on that repairman?

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:37.960
Nothing yet.

00:14:39.120 --> 00:14:41.960
The security camera at the main gate only caught him entering,

00:14:41.960 --> 00:14:42.960
but not leaving.

00:14:43.240 --> 00:14:43.840
Moreover,

00:14:43.840 --> 00:14:46.120
there's no camera at the back gate of that neighborhood.

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:46.840
I suspect

00:14:47.520 --> 00:14:49.180
he left through the back gate.

00:14:50.040 --> 00:14:51.240
Keep investigating.

00:14:51.360 --> 00:14:52.800
Both Xu Xing and Zhao Wenbing

00:14:52.800 --> 00:14:54.280
have alibis.

00:14:54.800 --> 00:14:56.320
But we can't rule out the possibility

00:14:56.320 --> 00:14:58.720
that one of them hired someone else to do it.

00:14:59.320 --> 00:15:00.780
There's another suspect.

00:15:01.680 --> 00:15:02.280
Wang Min.

00:15:02.920 --> 00:15:03.320
Yeah.

00:15:04.280 --> 00:15:05.600
Lin Ran and Li Xiaoru

00:15:05.840 --> 00:15:07.360
were both murdered one after another.

00:15:07.360 --> 00:15:08.800
And both of them

00:15:09.040 --> 00:15:10.970
had sexual relations with Xu Xing.

00:15:11.640 --> 00:15:12.960
Hey, Master, do you think

00:15:12.960 --> 00:15:15.080
it could be Xu Xing's wife,

00:15:15.080 --> 00:15:16.340
Wang Min, who did this?

00:15:17.840 --> 00:15:19.280
There's another suspect.

00:15:19.280 --> 00:15:19.760
Another one?

00:15:19.760 --> 00:15:20.560
More?

00:15:22.160 --> 00:15:23.820
I found a deleted text message

00:15:24.280 --> 00:15:25.760
in Li Xiaoru's phone,

00:15:26.440 --> 00:15:28.040
just like the one Lin Ran got.

00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:29.560
The only difference is

00:15:30.520 --> 00:15:32.720
she is the second villain to be judged.

00:15:34.760 --> 00:15:36.890
This is a bit different from Lin Ran's.

00:15:40.400 --> 00:15:41.320
Xu Xing said

00:15:42.040 --> 00:15:45.000
they played a LARP game a week ago.

00:15:46.040 --> 00:15:47.480
In that game,

00:15:48.280 --> 00:15:50.360
Lin Ran was the first to fall to his death,

00:15:50.360 --> 00:15:52.490
then Li Xiaoru was the second to drown.

00:15:53.600 --> 00:15:56.000
Finally, Zhao Wenbing and Xu Xing died too.

00:15:56.520 --> 00:15:57.000
Now,

00:15:57.560 --> 00:15:59.690
only Zhao Wenbing and Xu Xing are left.

00:16:01.560 --> 00:16:02.560
Then it seems

00:16:03.640 --> 00:16:05.360
this is no ordinary ad.

00:16:05.480 --> 00:16:06.760
It's a death notice.

00:16:08.280 --> 00:16:09.640
The suspect you mentioned

00:16:09.640 --> 00:16:11.320
is the one who sent the texts,

00:16:11.360 --> 00:16:14.360
and this person is very likely the LARP game designer.

00:16:14.840 --> 00:16:15.640
That's right.

00:16:20.720 --> 00:16:22.360
I had Cybersecurity look into it.

00:16:22.360 --> 00:16:23.120
They said

00:16:23.400 --> 00:16:26.260
the sender used multiple overseas proxy accounts.

00:16:26.480 --> 00:16:28.080
It'll take some time to track them down.

00:16:28.080 --> 00:16:28.940
I'll follow up.

00:16:31.040 --> 00:16:32.900
I'm going to go see Wang Min again.

00:16:33.360 --> 00:16:35.040
Go investigate the murder mystery venue.

00:16:35.040 --> 00:16:36.080
I'll go with him.

00:16:36.480 --> 00:16:37.400
On his own,

00:16:37.680 --> 00:16:38.840
he probably won't find anything.

00:16:38.840 --> 00:16:39.480
I...

00:16:41.160 --> 00:16:41.920
Go.

00:16:45.480 --> 00:16:46.440
Hey, Chen.

00:16:46.520 --> 00:16:47.560
For trivial things like this in the future,

00:16:47.560 --> 00:16:48.280
I can handle it.

00:16:48.280 --> 00:16:50.210
You really don't need to tag along.

00:16:50.600 --> 00:16:52.200
What I see and what you see

00:16:52.800 --> 00:16:53.880
seem to be different.

00:16:53.880 --> 00:16:54.640
Ah.

00:16:54.920 --> 00:16:56.680
Hey, are you calling me stupid?

00:16:58.520 --> 00:16:59.200
Hello.

00:17:01.720 --> 00:17:03.160
I'm from the Criminal Investigation Brigade.

00:17:03.160 --> 00:17:05.119
We have a case that requires your cooperation.

00:17:05.119 --> 00:17:06.599
Okay, I'm the owner here.

00:17:06.599 --> 00:17:07.730
What can I do for you?

00:17:09.440 --> 00:17:10.240
Did your store

00:17:10.599 --> 00:17:11.930
send this text message?

00:17:14.680 --> 00:17:15.319
No.

00:17:15.480 --> 00:17:16.960
Who even reads text messages nowadays?

00:17:16.960 --> 00:17:18.480
It wouldn't achieve any promotional effect.

00:17:18.480 --> 00:17:19.609
We've never sent it.

00:17:22.680 --> 00:17:23.960
Are there surveillance cameras

00:17:23.960 --> 00:17:24.960
in your rooms?

00:17:25.520 --> 00:17:25.920
No.

00:17:26.200 --> 00:17:28.680
Customers today care a lot about privacy.

00:17:34.880 --> 00:17:35.200
Hey.

00:17:36.360 --> 00:17:37.640
Do you have records

00:17:37.640 --> 00:17:39.370
of the winning and losing order

00:17:39.400 --> 00:17:40.360
for your murder mystery games?

00:17:40.360 --> 00:17:43.080
Our hosts run over ten games a day on average.

00:17:43.720 --> 00:17:44.980
It's been so many days.

00:17:45.080 --> 00:17:46.810
They probably don't remember.

00:17:48.160 --> 00:17:48.890
Understood.

00:17:49.840 --> 00:17:50.480
Then please

00:17:50.480 --> 00:17:51.560
give me a copy of

00:17:52.040 --> 00:17:53.570
the Death Descends script.

00:17:53.720 --> 00:17:54.160
Sure.

00:17:57.360 --> 00:17:58.360
Here you go.

00:18:02.720 --> 00:18:05.320
Did you write this script yourselves,

00:18:05.520 --> 00:18:06.640
or did you buy it?

00:18:07.160 --> 00:18:08.760
It was written by someone a friend recommended.

00:18:08.760 --> 00:18:10.160
We bought out the rights.

00:18:10.440 --> 00:18:11.280
Have you met the author?

00:18:11.280 --> 00:18:12.600
Do you have their contact info?

00:18:12.600 --> 00:18:13.460
Never met them.

00:18:13.640 --> 00:18:15.240
We only communicate online.

00:18:18.320 --> 00:18:18.800
Okay.

00:18:18.920 --> 00:18:20.650
We'll take this with us for now.

00:18:21.360 --> 00:18:22.160
Thanks for your trouble.

00:18:22.160 --> 00:18:22.760
Take care.

00:18:28.480 --> 00:18:29.040
Mrs. Xu.

00:18:29.040 --> 00:18:30.240
Don't call me Mrs. Xu.

00:18:30.320 --> 00:18:31.380
My name is Wang Min.

00:18:34.200 --> 00:18:34.730
Ms. Wang.

00:18:38.400 --> 00:18:39.330
These two women,

00:18:39.800 --> 00:18:40.440
do you know them?